    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>Claire Seaman is a Professor in Enterprise and Family Business. She has published over 30 journal articles on family businesses in the UK, New Zealand and Latin America and is a regular contributor to family business conferences worldwide. Her recent book, The Modern Family Business, was developed with colleagues and published by Palgrave McMillan.</p>]]></Value>
